videos.headline: Texas electrifies with 75-yard TD on opening play
videos.description: Texas QB Casey Thompson quickly passes to Xavier Worthy, who then speeds 75 yards downfield and into the end zone for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Texas electrifies with 75-yard TD on opening play) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bijan Robinson's TD puts Longhorns up two scores early
videos.description: Texas RB Bijan Robinson gets the handoff and finds his way across the goal line for the touchown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bijan Robinson's TD puts Longhorns up two scores early) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Xavier Worthy lays out for incredible diving catch
videos.description: Texas QB Casey Thompson sends the ball toward Xavier Worthy, who gets by a defender and makes a diving grab.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Xavier Worthy lays out for incredible diving catch) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caleb Williams' TD pass helps keep Oklahoma close
videos.description: Oklahoma QB Caleb Williams finds Marvin Mims for a 14-yard TD to keep the Sooners in the game.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Caleb Williams' TD pass helps keep Oklahoma close) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kennedy Brooks finds a hole for go-ahead Oklahoma TD
videos.description: Oklahoma RB Kennedy Brooks gets the handoff and rushes 18 yards for a touchdown, putting the Sooners ahead of the Texas Longhorns.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Kennedy Brooks finds a hole for go-ahead Oklahoma TD) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Xavier Worthy makes leaping TD grab to tie game for Texas
videos.description: Texas QB Casey Thompson flings it to Xavier Worthy, who makes a jumping catch for a touchdown to tie the game for the Longhorns.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Xavier Worthy makes leaping TD grab to tie game for Texas) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brooks breaks free for game-winning TD for Oklahoma
videos.description: Oklahoma RB Kennedy Brooks gets the handoff, rushes 33 yards and scores the game-winning touchdown with three seconds left.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brooks breaks free for game-winning TD for Oklahoma) 2021/10/09 ESHEET

videos.headline: Caleb Williams goes 66 yards for TD on fourth down
videos.description: Caleb Williams calls his own number on 4th-and-1 and rushes 66 yards for an Oklahoma touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Caleb Williams goes 66 yards for TD on fourth down) 2021/10/09 ESHEET
